msgstr "弯曲角度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:50
msgid "The amount of rotation."
msgstr "旋转量。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:51
msgid "Radius"
msgstr "半径"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:52
msgid "The sharpness of the bend."
msgstr "弯曲的锐利程度。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:59
msgid "Clamp"
msgstr "钳制"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:54
msgid ""
"Normally the arc turns through a clamped rotation angle with the "
"selected elements extended along a tangent line beyond that (see above "
"left). When the clamp is deactivated, the arc continues around aligning "
"the selected elements into a circle (right)."
msgstr ""
"通常弧形会在选中元素超出切线的角度停止(见上文左图)。当关闭钳制后，弧线会"
"继续绕圆周变形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:58
msgid ""
"When off :kbd:`Alt` all selected elements follow a circle, even when "
"outside the segment between the 3D cursor and the mouse."
msgstr ""
"当 :kbd:`Alt` 关闭钳制后，所有选中元素沿圆周变形，即使是超出3D游标和鼠标"
"之间的部分。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:63
msgid ""
"Unlike most other transform modes, *Bend* is not effected by *Pivot "
"Point* or *Transform Orientation*, always using the View Plane instead."
msgstr ""
"与其他变换模式不同，*弯曲* 不受 *轴心点* 或 *变换坐标系* 影响，总是在视图"
"平面上变形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:68
msgid ""
"You can turn the bend angle through multiple rotations potentially "
"forming a spiral shape."
msgstr "可以通过多次弯曲的旋转，形成螺旋形状。"

